      "text": "See [[Homeostasis]]\n\nA homeostat is a special kind of paired feedback loop. Two things are special 1) there is the embedded information on the limits of viability for the looped system and 2) the ability exists for action based on that information (making it knowledge). The homeostat has the effect of keeping the looped system within sustainable limits: Viability.\n"
    },
